const theme={
    light:{
        theme:'light',
        bg:'#FFFFFF',
        txt:'#212121',
        inputtxt:'#9E9E9E',
        disable:'#757575',
        disable1:'#424242',
        disable2:'#616161',
        border:'#EEEEEE',
        borderbg:'#FFFFFF',
        btn:'#EEEDFE',
        btntxt:'#584CF4',
        input:'#FAFAFA',
        barstyle: 'dark-content',
       
    },
    dark:{
        theme:'dark',
        bg:'#212121',
        txt:'#FFFFFF',
        inputtxt:'#FFFFFF',   
        disable:'#FFFFFF', 
        disable1:'#E0E0E0', 
        disable2:'#E0E0E0',
        border:'#35383F',
        borderbg:'#1F222A',
        btn:'#35383F',
        btntxt:'#FFFFFF',
        input:'#1F222A',
        barstyle:'light-content',
        
    },
    
};

export default theme;
